================================================================================

MODELS

FoodMapper downloads and runs ML models on-device. No model weights are
bundled in this repository. Users download models at runtime.

All models use the SafeTensors format for weight storage. FoodMapper does not
load pickle files or any other serialized Python objects.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

GTE-Large (General Text Embeddings)
https://huggingface.co/richtext/foodmapper-gte-large

MIT License (original model)

A 335M parameter BERT-based embedding model originally published by the
Institute for Intelligent Computing, Alibaba Group. The MLX-compatible
SafeTensors conversion used by FoodMapper is hosted at the repository above.
This is the primary model used for the research validation pipeline.

Original model: https://huggingface.co/thenlper/gte-large

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Qwen3-Embedding (0.6B / 4B / 8B)
https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3-Embedding-0.6B

Apache License 2.0

Copyright (c) 2025 Alibaba Cloud / Qwen Team.

Text embedding models from the Qwen3 family. Available in three sizes for
different hardware profiles. MLX-quantized (DWQ 4-bit) SafeTensors weights
are provided by mlx-community on HuggingFace. Used as the embedding stage
in the standard food matching pipeline. Requires enabling advanced options.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Qwen3-Reranker (0.6B / 4B)
https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3-Reranker-0.6B

Apache License 2.0

Copyright (c) 2025 Alibaba Cloud / Qwen Team.

Cross-encoder reranker models from the Qwen3 family. MLX-converted SafeTensors
weights are hosted on HuggingFace. Used as the second stage in two-stage and
smart triage pipelines. Requires enabling advanced options.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Qwen3 (0.6B / 4B) -- Generative Judge
https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3-0.6B

Apache License 2.0

Copyright (c) 2025 Alibaba Cloud / Qwen Team.

General-purpose Qwen3 language models used in generative judge mode for
match selection via logit extraction. MLX-quantized (4-bit) SafeTensors
weights are provided by mlx-community. Experimental. Requires advanced options.

================================================================================

EXTERNAL SERVICES

FoodMapper optionally connects to external APIs. These are not bundled
dependencies but are used at runtime when configured by the user.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Anthropic Claude API
https://www.anthropic.com

Used in the research validation pipeline (GTE-Large + Claude Haiku hybrid).
Requires the user to provide their own Anthropic API key. Communication uses
the Anthropic Message Batches API. No API keys are stored in this repository.
